lead_paragraph: Michael Wacha gave up one run over two innings in his first start of the exhibition season as the St. Louis Cardinals beat a Minnesota Twins' split squad 5-3 Tuesday.

headline.main: Cardinals' Wacha Gives Up 1 Run in Spring Training Debut
